enum.name: CatOutPutFormatType
enum.abstract: Output format of the Knowledge Expert text report.

enum.name: CatShowResultType
enum.abstract: Sorting option for the Expert Knowledge text report.

enum.name: CatSolveType
enum.abstract: Type for controlling the resolution in Knowledge Expert.

enum.name: CatVisualizationType
enum.abstract: Type of checks to be chosen for the Expert Knowledge Report.

class.name: ExpertCheck
class.abstract: Represents the edition part of a check.

method.name: Body
method.abstract: Returns or sets the body of a Check.

method.name: Language
method.abstract: Returns or sets the language of a check.

method.name: Variables
method.abstract: Returns or sets the variable scope of an Expert Check.

method.name: Correct
method.abstract: Applies the "correction" function on failed elements.

method.name: Highlight
method.abstract: Highlights the Failures on the check.

method.name: Status
method.abstract: Returns the Status of the check.

method.name: AutomaticCorrect
method.abstract: Returns or sets the status of the automatic correction facility.

method.name: CheckEdition
method.abstract: Returns the editable object corresponding to this check.

method.name: CorrectFunction
method.abstract: Returns or sets the body to be called in order to correct the check.

method.name: CorrectFunctionComment
method.abstract: Returns or sets the comment of the correct function of the check.

method.name: CorrectFunctionType
method.abstract: Returns or sets the type of the body to be called in order to correct the check.

method.name: Failures
method.abstract: Returns the list of the tuples that don't satisfy this check.

method.name: Help
method.abstract: Returns or sets the contextual help of the check object.

method.name: Justification
method.abstract: Returns or sets the reason why the check was overridden.

method.name: Priority
method.abstract: Returns or sets the priority of the check.

method.name: Succeeds
method.abstract: Returns the list of the tuples that satisfy this check.

method.name: getTuple
method.abstract: Returns a tuple (a collection of objects) concerned by this report object.

method.name: getTupleSize
method.abstract: Returns the size of the tuple concerned by this report object.

method.name: Validity
method.abstract: Returns the validity of a check for a given tuple.

class.name: ExpertReportObjects
class.abstract: Represents the collection of (succeeded or failed) report objects.

method.name: FailItem
method.abstract: Retrieves a report failed component from a failed tuples collection, using its index or its name from the Check collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Retrieves a Report component using its index or its name from the Check collection.

method.name: SucceedItem
method.abstract: Retrieves a report component from a succeeded tuples collection, using its index or its name from the Check collection.

method.name: CountFail
method.abstract: Returns the number of failed tuples in the failed tuples collection.

method.name: CountSucceed
method.abstract: Returns the number of succeeded tuples in the succeeded tuples collection.

class.name: ExpertRule
class.abstract: Represents the edition part of a rule.

method.name: Body
method.abstract: Returns or sets the string that defines the body of a Rule.

method.name: Language
method.abstract: Returns or sets the language of a rule.

method.name: Variables
method.abstract: Returns or sets the variables scope of the a Rule.

class.name: ExpertRuleBase
class.abstract: Represents the RuleBase object that can be edited.

method.name: VolatileCopy
method.abstract: Copy the persistent rulebase in a unpersistent unchangeable rulebase.

class.name: ExpertRuleBaseComponentRuntime
class.abstract: Represents a rule base component in a ruleset.

method.name: AccurateType
method.abstract: Returns as a string the type of component.

method.name: Activate
method.abstract: Activates the RuleBaseComponent.

method.name: Deactivate
method.abstract: Desactivates the RuleBaseComponent.

method.name: IsUseOnly
method.abstract: Retrieves the use-only status of the component.

method.name: Isactivate
method.abstract: Tells if the RuleBaseComponent is active.

method.name: Parse
method.abstract: Syntactically analyses (ie parses) the component.

method.name: SetUseOnly
method.abstract: Prevents any access to the component for reading or deleting.

method.name: Comment
method.abstract: Returns or sets the comment of a rulebase component.

class.name: ExpertRuleBaseComponentRuntimes
class.abstract: Represents the collection of ExpertRuleBase (ExpertChecks, ExpertRules, and ExpertRuleSets) components.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a RuleBase component using its index or its name from the entire RuleBase collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes an Expert component from the Rule Base collection.

method.name: ShallowCount
method.abstract: Returns the number of first-level-depth objects in the collection.

method.name: ShallowItem
method.abstract: Returns a first-level-depth RuleBase component using its index or its name from the RuleBase collection.

method.name: ShallowRemove
method.abstract: Removes an first-level-depth Expert component from the Rule Base collection.

class.name: ExpertRuleBaseRuntime
class.abstract: Represents the Runtime part of the RuleBase.

method.name: AccurateType
method.abstract: Returns as a string the type of component.

method.name: AddFact
method.abstract: Adds new fact to the rule base resolution.

method.name: AddRootOfFacts
method.abstract: Adds a new root of facts to the rule base.

method.name: Deduce
method.abstract: Launch a Forward chaining Solve on the current RuleBase.

method.name: Fingerprint
method.abstract: Returns the Fingerprint information.

method.name: GetNumberOfRootsOfFacts
method.abstract: Retrieves the number of roots of facts of the rule base.

method.name: GetRootsOfFacts
method.abstract: Retrieves all the roots of facts from the rule base.

method.name: Import
method.abstract: Import from RuleSet.

method.name: ImportFromFile
method.abstract: Import from file.

method.name: ImportWithLink
method.abstract: Import with link to a document.

method.name: RemoveRootOfFacts
method.abstract: Removes a root of facts from the rule base.

method.name: Report
method.abstract: Launch a Report.

method.name: SynchronizeStatus
method.abstract: Returns the Synchronize information.

method.name: ReportDescriptionLength
method.abstract: Returns or sets the Report Description Length (For Text option only).

method.name: ReportOutPutFormat
method.abstract: Returns or sets the Report OutPut Format.

method.name: ReportPath
method.abstract: Returns or sets the Report output path.

method.name: ReportShowResult
method.abstract: Returns or sets the option for sorting the report.

method.name: RuleBaseEdition
method.abstract: Returns the editable object corresponding to this rulebase.

method.name: RuleSet
method.abstract: Returns the Set linked to the RuleBase.

method.name: SolveType
method.abstract: Returns or sets the solve option.

method.name: TextVisualization
method.abstract: Returns or sets the Report option for visualization.

method.name: Priority
method.abstract: Returns or sets the priority of the rule.

method.name: RuleEdition
method.abstract: Returns the editable object corresponding to this rule.

class.name: ExpertRuleSet
class.abstract: Represents the ExpertRuleSet object which is the editable part of a RuleSet or a RuleBase.

method.name: CreateCheck
method.abstract: Creates a check and adds it to the RuleSet.

method.name: CreateRule
method.abstract: Creates a rule and adds it to the RuleSet.

method.name: CreateRuleSet
method.abstract: Creates a RuleSet and adds it to the RuleSet.

class.name: ExpertRuleSetRuntime
class.abstract: Represents the ExpertRuleSet object in the RelationSet.

method.name: Status
method.abstract: Returns the Status of the ruleset: 1=OK, 0=KO.

method.name: ExpertRuleBaseComponentRuntimes
method.abstract: Returns the list of the RuleBaseComponent.

method.name: RuleSetEdition
method.abstract: Returns the editable object corresponding to this ruleset.
